    {
      "id": "t29",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Twitch income comes from four main sources: subscriptions (50% split with Twitch for most partners), Bits (virtual currency at $0.01/bit), ad revenue (~$2–$4 CPM on ad-viewing viewers), and direct donations through PayPal or third-party tools."
    },
